flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Scheduled model refresh or detection of new candidate feature via 'Determine New Features and Update Process' (periodic cadence or feature discovery event).]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers + STREAMS - Ingest normalized transactional, WMS, TMS and external signal feeds into Subject Areas via DDM/Crawlers and STREAMS]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Data Quality & Validation - Run automated data quality and validation rules on ingested data and flag exceptions]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Enrich features (COGS, lifecycle, promotions, lead times) and train/evaluate forecasts with Cortex Auto Forecast (explainability via SHAP)]
  N3 --> N4{PB: Process Builder - Orchestrate decision flow in Process Builder to present add/retain/remove feature recommendation via CWB Lifecycle UI Screen}
  N4 -->|Primary| N5[PB: Remote Functions - If approved, execute Remote Functions to write feature/config updates and forecast adjustments to S4/Kinaxis and trigger Safety Stock Service recalculation]
  N5 --> N6[PB: UI Screens - Surface updated forecasts, impact dashboards and audit trail via UI Screens and Subject Areas for planner review]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Selected feature set applied to production forecasts resulting in measurable MAPE improvement, reduced stockouts and overstocks, optimized safety stock and replenishment signals, and verified neutral-or-positive revenue impact; automated rollback/hold if negative impact detected.]
  N4 -->|Automated data quality checks fail or...| B1[Process Builder creates Action Item and Notification; CWB Lifecycle marks feature decision as on-hold and routes to data ops for remediation]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Feature update deferred until data gaps resolved; prevents degraded model deployment]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|New feature yields statistically sign...| B2[Process Builder triggers auto-approve rules and schedules production retrain + writeback via Remote Functions]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Feature added to production forecasts with automated downstream updates and monitoring]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|Feature improves demand fit but simul...| B3[CWB Lifecycle flags finance review; Process Builder requires manual approval and runs additional constrained simulations via Remote Functions]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Decision requires stakeholder override; protects revenue and prevents unintended inventory/waste consequences]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]